stat

public static void stat(java.lang.Object key,
                        java.lang.Number val)
Wrapper around Scrivener's stat API. Attaches timestamp automatically before sending to server

Parameters:
key - A unique key identifying the statistic metric. Ideally maintain a global enum of stat-keys
val - A value to denote the metric. Call with value=1 to denote a counter call
